### Get user stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/me/stats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Create invitation from first user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Check if invitation is valid
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invitations/{{code}}

