### Create a lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "name": "Desert Match",
  "description": "Fremen training game in Arrakis",
  "max_players": 2,
  "rounds": 2,
  "ante": 1
}

### sse events for lobby with id 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/events

### get lobby with id 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### List all lobbies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/all

### List all available lobbies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/available

### Second user joins the lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/2/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### Second user leaves the lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### delete lobby with id 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/delete
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Start the match
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/2/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Start first round
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/3/rounds/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Player 1 plays first turn - first roll
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/3/turns/play
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Player 1 plays first turn - rerolls
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/play
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "kept_dice": [false, false, false, false, false]
}

### Get current match state
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/39

### Get current round state after Player 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Player 1 passes turn
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/pass
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Player 2 plays first turn - first roll
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/play
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Player 2 plays first turn - reroll
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/play
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kept_dice": [true, false, true, true, true]
}

### Get current round state after Player 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### Get current round state after Player 1 passes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Player 2 passes turn
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/pass
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### Get current round state after Player 2 passes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### Finish the round (host)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/finish
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Get current match state
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1

### Start next round
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

