Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kept_dice": [false, false, false, false, false]
}

### Player 1 passes turn
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/pass
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Get current round state after Player 1 in round 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/rounds/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Player 2 plays turn in round 2 - first roll
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/turns/play
